name: Introduction to C Programming
details: Learn the fundamentals of the C programming language, including syntax, variables, loops, and functions. Develop your skills in writing basic C programs.

name: Introduction to Algorithms
details: Dive into the world of algorithms and problem-solving techniques. Understand how algorithms work and how to analyze their efficiency. Develop critical thinking skills for algorithm design.

name: Introduction to C++ for DSA
details: Explore the basics of C++ programming, including object-oriented concepts, classes, inheritance, and polymorphism. Begin building proficiency in C++ development.

name: Basic Data Structures
details: Explore essential data structures like arrays, linked lists, stacks, and queues. Understand how to implement and manipulate these structures in various programming languages.

name: Introduction to OOP Python
details: Discover Python, a versatile and beginner-friendly programming language. Learn Python syntax, data types, and how to write scripts and applications.

name: Software Engineering
details: Learn the principles and practices of software development, including software lifecycle, design patterns, testing, and project management. Understand how to build robust and maintainable software.

name: AWS, Cloud Computing
details: Get introduced to cloud computing and AWS services. Learn how to deploy and manage applications in the AWS cloud environment, including EC2 instances, S3 storage, and more.

name: Database (MySQL)
details: Gain knowledge in database management using MySQL. Learn how to design and query relational databases, manage data, and work with SQL.

name: Problem-Solving Part
details: Hone your problem-solving skills by tackling programming challenges and puzzles. Learn strategies and techniques to approach complex coding problems efficiently.
